{"title_page": "List of fictional shared universes in film and television", "text_new": "==Film==\nThis is a '''list of shared universes''' in film. There are different definitions of [[shared universe]]. It is a requirement that two or more previously unconnected characters come together into one film.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Universe\n! Origin film\n! Start date\n! End date\n! Connecting characters\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Universal Monsters#Recurring cast and characters|Universal Monsters]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Dracula (1931 English-language film)|Dracula]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1931\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1951\n| ''[[Dracula (1931 English-language film)|Dracula]]'', ''[[Frankenstein (1931 film)|Frankenstein]]'', ''[[The Invisible Man (1933 film)|The Invisible Man]]'' and ''[[The Wolf Man (1941 film)|The Wolf Man]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Toho]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Godzilla (1954 film)|Godzilla]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1954\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1975\n| ''[[Godzilla]], [[Rodan]], [[Mothra]], [[Baragon]], and [[Manda_(kaiju)|Manda]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Alien vs. Predator]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Alien (film)|Alien]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1979\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[Alien (franchise)|Alien]]'' and ''[[Predator (franchise)|Predator]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Freddy vs. Jason]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Friday the 13th (1980 film)|Friday the 13th]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1980\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2003\n| ''[[Friday the 13th (franchise)|Jason Voorhees]]'' and ''[[A Nightmare on Elm Street (franchise)|Freddy Krueger]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Full Moon Features]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Puppet Master (film)|Puppet Master]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1989\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2016\n| ''[[Demonic Toys]]'', ''[[Puppet Master (franchise)|Puppet Master]]'', ''[[Dollman (film)|Dollman]]'' and ''[[Bad Channels]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[View Askewniverse]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Clerks]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1994\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| [[Jay and Silent Bob]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[Lake Placid vs. Anaconda]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Anaconda (film)|Anaconda]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1997\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2015\n| ''[[Anaconda (film series)|Anaconda]]'' and ''[[Lake Placid (film series)|Lake Placid]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Sadako vs. Kayako]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Ring (film)|Ring]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1998\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2016\n| ''[[The Ring (franchise)|The Ring (Japanese films)]]'' and ''[[Ju-On (franchise)|Ju-On (Japanese films)]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Unbreakable (film series)|''Unbreakable'' film series]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Unbreakable (film)|Unbreakable]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2000\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2019\n| [[Unbreakable (film)|David Dunn]], [[Split (2016 American film)|Kevin Wendell Crumb]] and [[Glass (2019 film)|Elijah Price / Mr. Glass]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Marvel Cinematic Universe]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Iron Man (2008 film)|Iron Man]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2008\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[Iron Man (2008 film)|Iron Man]]'', ''[[The Incredible Hulk (film)|Hulk]]'', ''[[Thor (film)|Thor]]'', ''[[Captain America: The First Avenger|Captain America]]'', ''[[The Avengers (2012 film)|The Avengers]]'', ''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (film)|The Guardians of the Galaxy]]'', ''[[Ant-Man (film)|Ant-Man]]'', ''[[Ant-Man and the Wasp|Wasp]]'', ''[[Doctor Strange (2016 film)|Doctor Strange]]'', ''[[Spider-Man: Homecoming|Spider