on King (film series)|The Scorpion King]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[X-Men (film series)|X-Men]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[X-Men (film)|X-Men]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2000\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2020\n| ''[[X-Men (film)|X-Men]]'', ''[[Wolverine (film series)|Wolverine]]'' and ''[[Deadpool (film series)|Deadpool]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Middle-earth (film franchise)|Middle-earth]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2001\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2014\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|The Lord of the Rings]]'' and ''[[The Hobbit (film series)|The Hobbit]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Wizarding World]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone (film)|Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2001\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[Harry Potter (film series)|Harry Potter]]'' and ''[[Wizarding World|Fantastic Beasts]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Cars (franchise)|Cars]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Cars (film)|Cars]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2006\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[Cars (film)|Cars]]'' and ''[[Planes (film)|Planes]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)|Despicable Me]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Despicable Me]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2010\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[Despicable Me]]'' and ''[[Minions (film)|Minions]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[The Conjuring Universe]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[The Conjuring]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2013\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Present\n| ''[[The Conjuring]]'', ''[[Annabelle (film)|Annabelle]]'', ''[[The Nun (2018 film)|The Nun]]'' and ''[[The Curse of La Llorona]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: