017 TV series)|Riverdale]]''\n|2017 \u2014 present\n| ''[[Riverdale (2017 TV series)|Riverdale]]'', ''[[Chilling Adventures of Sabrina (TV series)|Chilling Adventures of Sabrina]]'' and ''[[Katy Keene (TV series)|Katy Keene]]''\n|-\n| ''[[Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse]]'' and ''[[Spider-Man (1967 TV series)|Spider-Man]]'' (1967)\n| ''[[Spider-Man (1967 TV series)|Spider-Man]]'' (1967)\n|2018 \u2014 present\n|\n|-\n| [[Marvel Cinematic Universe]] [[List of Marvel Cinematic Universe television series|Television Series]]\n| ''[[Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.]]''\n|2013 - present\n|''[[Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.]]'', ''[[Agent Carter (TV series)|Agent Carter]]'', ''[[Daredevil (TV series)|Daredevil]]'', ''[[Jessica Jones (TV series)|Jessica Jones]]'', ''[[Luke Cage (TV series)|Luke Cage]]'', ''[[Iron Fist (TV series)|Iron Fist]]'', ''[[The Defenders (miniseries)|The Defenders]]'', ''[[Inhumans (TV series)|Inhumans]]'', ''[[The Punisher (TV series)|The Punisher]]'', ''[[Runaways (TV series)|Runaways]]'', ''[[Cloak & Dagger (TV series)|Cloak & Dagger]]'', ''[[Helstrom (TV series)|Helstrom]],'' ''[[The Falcon and the Winter Soldier]], [[WandaVision]] and [[Loki (Marvel Cinematic Universe)|Loki]]''\n|-\n| [[Aris Nugraha]]'s Universe\n| ''[[Preman Pensiun]]''\n|2015 \u2014 present\n|''[[Preman Pensiun]]'', ''[[Tukang Ojek Pengkolan]]'', ''[[Awas Banyak Copet!]]'', ''{{ill|Gober (TV series)|lt=Gober|id|Gober}}'', ''[[Preman Pensiun (film)|Preman Pensiun]]'', and many short films and television specials. An Indonesian [[comedy series]] produced by [[Aris Nugraha Production]] and [[MNC Pictures]].\n|-\n| ''[[American Crime Story]]''\n| ''[[The People v. O. J. Simpson: American Crime Story]]''\n|2016 \u2014 present\n| An American [[true crime]] [[anthology series]] developed by [[Scott Alexander and Larry Karaszewski]], who are executive producers with [[Brad Falchuk]], [[Nina Jacobson]], [[Ryan Murphy (writer)|Ryan Murphy]], and Brad Simpson.\n|-\n| ''[[Looney Tunes]]''\n| ''[[Looney Tunes]]''\n|1930 - present\n|''[[Looney Tunes]]'', ''[[Merrie Melodies]]'', ''[[Tiny Toon Adventures]]'', ''[[Animaniacs]]'', ''[[Pinky and the Brain]]'', ''[[Freakazoid!]]'',  ''[[Road Rovers]]'' and ''[[Histeria!]]''\n|-\n| [[Titansverse]]\n| ''[[Titans (2018 TV series)|Titans]]''\n|2018 \u2014 present\n|''[[Titans (2018 TV series)|Titans]]'', ''[[Doom Patrol (TV series)|Doom Patrol]]''\n|-\n| ''[[Cow and Chicken]]'' and ''[[I Am Weasel]]''\n|\n| 1997 - present\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Grim & Evil]]'' franchise, ''[[Ed, Edd n Eddy]]'' and ''[[Codename: Kids Next Door]]''\n|\n| 2001 - present\n|\n|-\n| [[Ben 10 (franchise)|''Ben 10'' franchise]], ''[[Generator Rex]]'' and ''[[The Secret Saturdays]]''\n|\n| 2005 - present\n|[[Generator Rex]] in the same multiverse\n|-\n| [[Jay Ward]] Universe\n| ''[[Rocky and Bullwinkle]]''\n|1959 - present\n| (''[[Rocky and Bullwinkle]]'', ''[[Dudley Do-Right]]'', ''[[George of the Jungle]]'' and ''[[Fractured Fairy Tales]]'')\n|-\n| ''[[Yu-Gi-Oh!]]''\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| ''[[2 Stupid Dogs]]'', ''[[Dexter's Laboratory]]'', ''[[The Powerpuff Girls]]'', ''[[Samurai Jack]]'', ''[[Foster's Home for Imaginary Friends]]'' and ''[[Sym-Bionic Titan]]''\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[4Kids TV|The Fight for the Fox Box]]\n|\n|\n| ''[[Sonic X]]'', ''[[Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles (2003 TV series)|Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles]]'', ''[[Kirby: Right Back at Ya!]]'' and ''[[Cubix: Robots for Everyone]]''\n|-\n|[[The Official BBC Children in Need Medley]]\n|\n|\n| ''[[Thomas & Friends]]'', ''[[Bob the Builder]]'', ''[[Postman Pat]]'', ''[[Fireman Sam]]'', ''[[Pingu]]'', ''[[Rubbadubbers]]'', ''[[Angelina Ballerina (TV series)|Angelina Ballerina]]'', ''[[The Koala Brothers]]'', ''[[Roary the Racing Car]]'', ''[[Fifi and the Flowertots]]'', ''[[Little Robots]]'', ''[[Muffin the Mule]]'', ''[[Flower Pot Men]]'', ''[[Andy Pandy]]'', ''[[BBC Children in Need|Children in Need]]'', ''[[Engie Benjy]]'', ''[[Paddington (TV series)|Paddington Bear]]'', ''[[The Wombles]]'', ''[[Teletubbie