nfections confirmed in S'pore, majority are work permit holders in dorms |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/new-high-of-942-covid-19-infections-confirmed-majority-are-work-permit-holders-in-dorms |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=19 April 2020 |date=18 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Yang |first1=Calvin |title=New high of 942 Covid-19 infections confirmed, taking tally close to 6,000 cases |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/new-high-of-942-covid-19-infections-confirmed-taking-tally-close-to-6000-cases |website=The Straits Times |accessdate=19 April 2020 |date=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n\nThroughout the outbreak, several clusters were discovered; namely the Life Church and Missions Singapore, Yong Thai Hang health products shop, a business meeting at Grand Hyatt hotel,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/novel-coronavirus-3-new-cases-confirmed-all-have-not-recently-travelled-china|title=3 Novel coronavirus: 3 new cases confirmed, all have not recently travelled to China|date=9 February 2020|website=TODAYonline|access-date=9 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200210152715/https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/novel-coronavirus-3-new-cases-confirmed-all-have-not-recently-travelled-china|archive-date=10 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> the 10 Seletar Aerospace Heights construction site, the [[Grace Assembly of God]],<ref name=\"13FebMOH\">{{cite web |title=Eight More Confirmed Cases of COVID-19 Infection |work=MOH |url=https://www.moh.gov.sg/news-highlights/details/eight-more-confirmed-cases-of-covid-19-infection |accessdate=13 February 2020 |date=13 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213114302/https://www.moh.gov.sg/news-highlights/details/eight-more-confirmed-cases-of-covid-19-infection |archive-date=13 February 2020 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Wizlearn Technologies (an e-learning firm at [[Singapore Science Park]]),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapo